ionary approach with access to a wide range of collective funds like unit and investment trusts discretionary investment management with expert service based on collective funds not individual securities designed for cash lump sums or existing portfolios from £ to £ six riskadjusted investment objectives spanning high to lowrisk portfolios flexibility to encompass general isa sipp and offshore portfolios our approach our team model portfolios fees and charges our approach our master portfolio service mps is a discretionary service that’s designed around simplicity and diversity as a segregated service it allows you to invest in a variety of collective funds rather than individual shares this means that you own the underlying units in each fund keeping you more closely involved with the funds that underpin your investment our team mps is managed by a dedicated investment team with more than  years experience our investment managers work closely with our research department to make decisions about the best blend of funds and asset allocation for each model portfolio what’s more we keep administration as simple and clear as possible we’ll give you a composite tax voucher at the end of the tax year and a sixmonthly valuation and portfolio review for more regular reviews of your portfolio log in to view your online portfolio valuation model portfolios we help you choose from a range of six defined model portfolios growth balanced income cautious defensive high growth each model contains a wide range of unit trusts investment trusts and openended investment companies oeics with each one representing a different style of investing furthermore mps also offers an offshore solution with nonuk domiciled models fees and charges when we buy the underlying funds on your behalf you’ll find the costs are often lower than the initial charges you’d typically face if you bought them directly youll also benefit from lower ongoing underlying charges because we’re able to negotiate institutional rates on your behalf for further information download our master portfolio service rate card how to apply call matthew salmon on    or send an email we’ll ask you some questions about your financial situation and investment objectives once your application is approved we will set up an initial meeting with an investment manager the value of investments and the income derived from them can go up as well as down and you may not get back your initial investment contact our master portfolio service team matthew salmon senior investment director matthew salmon senior investment director address work  gresham street london london ecv qn united kingdom matthew salmon is responsible for the firms master portfolio service a multimanager fundoffunds offering he also maintains his own private client base and sits on the collectives research committee with responsibility for uk equity fund selection read full biography email me request call back wealth and investment log in register contact us find our offices and get to know the people who make our business successful contact us accessibility legal security advice contact us indices investor relations mobile site copyright investec  investment portfolio management  otris software ag for corporate groups for municipalities for private equities demo trust your investment portfolio management to an impartial process investment portfolio management software makes it easier to successfully manage your investment structures manage your investment portfolios with otris corporate you will gain a groupwide overview of all the information in your corporate group interconnections within the group structures are documented relationships within the individual companies are illustrated relationship histories become traceable and comprehensible serving as a basis for the development of your investment concepts from the perspective of a group of companies investment portfolios should achieve a financial return and contribute to the f