 within a group are jointly managed and the related appointments are coordinated across all representatives all relationships of this kind are interlinked so that you can view the data from different perspectives each person’s occupancy situation can be visually depicted using diagrams the individual committees’ meeting dates are recorded in a calendar so that scheduling conflicts can be detected early on on request the people involved can be reminded of their participation by email in addition you will find a wide range of documents in the committees’ digital folders such as the invitation with the agenda of the next meeting as well as rulings and minutes from previous meetings that have already been archived modern investment portfolio management for more transparency in the corporate group otris corporate provides you with fast and easy access to all your investment structures and corporate data it forms the basis for your strategic investment management reliable and transparent controlling within investment portfolio management the investment control feature integrated in otris corporate will support you in managing your investments it monitors and informs you about what the individual companies within the group contribute to achieve the agreed objectives integrative solution with local access rights with otris corporate we offer a groupwide integrated software solution with local access rights this creates a consistent information platform which is updated immediately after data is input important data from subsidiaries branches and investment portfolios can be seamlessly reported directly to the central corporate control which can use the data immediately all parties are thereby provided with the relevant information those responsible in the individual investment portfolios can view the data that is associated with their unit all the information within the investment network is available to corporate control for evaluation purposes etc a central integrative so