ive investing for children regular income this aggressive portfolio aims to generate a high level of capital growth by focusing on higherrisk areas like emerging markets and smaller companies this mediumrisk portfolio aims for a reasonable return with less volatility than more aggressive options this defensive portfolio aims for modest growth whilst minimising volatility though it can still fall in value children usually have a long investment horizon so this portfolio focuses on higherrisk areas with greater growth potential this income portfolio is designed to produce a good level of income with the potential to grow and keep pace with inflation how much do you want to invest lump sum min £ £ monthly amount min £ £ calculate we amend the number of funds according to the amount you want to invest this helps to ensure that you have a welldiversified portfolio please note this has not been tailored to your individual circumstances portfolio suggestion the following four funds have been selected by our awardwinning research team they dovetail well together to provide a readymade diversified portfolio with exciting growth potential you can invest in the portfolio as it stands but using the sliders you can tailor it to suit your needs if you want to add additional funds you can leave a cash weighting which can be invested as you wish please note that the minimum investment into each fund is £ lump sum or £ per month the following five funds have been selected by our awardwinning research team they dovetail well together to provide a readymade diversified portfolio with exciting growth potential you can invest in the portfolio as it stands but using the sliders you can tailor it to suit your needs if you want to add additional funds you can leave a cash weighting which can be invested as you wish please note that the minimum investment into each fund is £ lump sum or £ per month the following seven funds have been selected by our awardwinning research team they dovetail 