plan both large and small to benefit from broadbased and diversified investments diversification helps protect your investment from sudden downturns in individual shareholdings whilst providing consistent returns when markets are rising tax advantages your master investment plan is classified as a ‘single premium investmentlinked life insurance policy’ this means that under current arrangements when you cash in part or all of your plan in the future the proceeds are treated in the same way as other life insurance policies and is taxfree this makes master investment plan an ideal investment vehicle for long term savings especially if you would like to benefit from additional taxfree cash drawings from your master investment plan during retirement professional investment management no longer do you have to worry about what to buy or when zurich’s professional investment management team in malaysia has over  years’ experience in money management buying and selling stocks and shares bonds and placing funds in areas which secure the best rates of return in addition the team can tap into the diverse expertise and experience of investment professionals working for zurich around the globe this has resulted in thousands of investors making consistently good returns as policyholders of zurich your master investment plan provides professional money management around the clock freeing you to do the things you want to do and providing you with peace of mind choice of funds master investment plan offers a selection of funds to choose from under one plan to suit your individual investment requirements transferswitch facility master investment plan allows you to switch your investments from one fund to another whenever you need giving you ultimate control over your investment exposure death or total and permanent disability tpd benefit master investment plan will pay out a guaranteed death or total and permanent disability benefit in the unlikely event of something happening to you